Manufacturing Alliance Definitions

manufacturing_alliance.Rd

A subset of ANZSIC2006 which captures the Manufacturing Alliance definitions of manufacturing sub-sectors.

Usage

manufacturing_alliance

Format

manufacturing_alliance

A data frame with 166 rows and 9 columns:

anzsic_division_code

AZSIC 2006 Division Code

anzsic_division

ANZSIC 2006 Division Name

anzsic_subdivision_code

ANZSIC 2006 Subdivision Code

anzsic_subdivision

ANZSIC 2006 Subdivision Name

anzsic_group_code

ANZISC 2006 Group Code

anzsic_group

ANZSIC 2006 Group Name

anzsic_class_code

ANZSIC 2006 Class Code

anzsic_class

ANZSIC 2006 Class Name

sub_sector

Manufacturing Alliance Sub-Sector

@source https://manufacturingalliance.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Appendix-A-Defining-the-Manufacturing-Alliances-Workforce.pdf
